color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">톡톡이 버충 후 조금 기다렸다가 풀버</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 크라운 장탄 2스에 따라 다른데 내 기준 기다렸다가 풀버하면 다음 버스트 중에&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">잡몹이 쏘는 걸 크라운으로 막기 가능</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 해보면서 적당히 조절 할 것</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">처음 나오는 6마리 잡몹 랩처 잡기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">공중 랩처들 나오면 아무 엘리트 먼저 조준 사격</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 수니스 2스로 잡몹 죽임</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 레후로 뼈대 파츠 운좋게 때리면 빨리 죽이기 가능</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">한마리 죽이면 다른 엘리트 조준</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">버스트 끝날 때 잡몹 거의 다 잡혀있고 엘리트 체력 어느정도 까면 OK</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">2. 레후 - 나가 - 신데렐라</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce882fa1bd62531c0a64993133e134c29906eec9890097c0744724088056d78e00dd3bae3965c154cb92102c52c10a83da82333b6fd7ddd\" style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:400;\" alt=\"79f3c028e2f206a26d81f6e04f857368c2\"></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">빨간 동그라미 랩처 안잡혔으면 잡거나 엄폐시키고 버충 추천</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 뿡뿡이 나오고 크라운 보호막 사라지면서 저새끼 쏴서 의문사 당함</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">레이저 쏘는 엘리트 조준하다가 적당히 몇 대 치면 죽는데 바로 뿡뿡이 조준</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">크라운 20스택 잡몹 쏠 때 되게 해놨으면 그대로 사격</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">딜 남으면 엄폐후에 해도 상관 없을 듯</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">1마리 피 조절 해서 남겨둘 것</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">3. 나가로 피채우기</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">크라운 16~17 스택 만들기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">잡몹 쏠때 전체엄폐하기 (엄폐물 없는 니케 맞으면 리트)</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">남은 시간 20초 쯤에 잡몹 잡히게 하면 좋음</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">4. 보스 나오면 레후 - 크라운 - 수니스</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">전체 엄폐 시키고 크라운으로 적당히 스택 조절</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 장탄 관리</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce882fa1bd62531c0a64993133e134c29906eec9890097c0744724088056d78e00dd3bae3965c154cb92102cf2d44fa3ffd7563b6fd7ddd\" style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\" alt=\"78f3c028e2f206a26d81f6e447837d68ff\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">해마가 쏠 거 같을 때 19스택 정도 만들고 전체 엄폐 해제</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">보스 나오면 레후로 이동 하고 풀버&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">뿡뿡이 조준사격 하면 끝</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">빔 수니스만 바로 안맞으면 될 듯</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">신데렐라 버스트 안쓰는 이유</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 몹이 많아서 순차공격이 뿡뿡이에게 안들어 갈 수 있음</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 잡몹 몇 마리 잡으면 2번째 뿡뿡이 나와서 망함</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">수니스 대신 아인도 해봤는데 아인의 니어 페더 방무뎀 때문에 1뎀 뜨는 거는 넘길 수 있는데</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">보스에서 둘다 버스트 쓰면 잡몹 잡혀서 거의 불가능</span></p>",
